{
  "script_id": "hyperbolic-tiling",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "hyperbolic-tiling",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hyperbolic-tiling/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.63,
      "size": 42048,
      "text": "画家埃舍尔有一幅《极限圆》，无数天使与魔鬼向圆的边缘越缩越小。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hyperbolic-tiling",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hyperbolic-tiling/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "这幅画背后，藏着一个奇妙的世界，叫做双曲平面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hyperbolic-tiling",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hyperbolic-tiling/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "今天我们就在圆盘里，亲手铺满这种停不下来的镶嵌。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hyperbolic-tiling",
      "section_id": "plane",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "plane-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hyperbolic-tiling/plane-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "我们把整个双曲平面，装进一个单位圆盘里，这就是庞加莱圆盘模型。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hyperbolic-tiling",
      "section_id": "plane",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "plane-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hyperbolic-tiling/plane-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.54,
      "size": 40608,
      "text": "圆盘的边界代表无穷远，任何图形靠近它，看起来都会无限缩小。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hyperbolic-tiling",
      "section_id": "plane",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "plane-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hyperbolic-tiling/plane-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "这里的直线不再笔直，而是垂直于边界圆的一段段圆弧。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hyperbolic-tiling",
      "section_id": "tiling",
      "line_id": "pq-2",
      "filename": "tiling-pq-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hyperbolic-tiling/tiling-pq-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.45,
      "size": 39168,
      "text": "在平坦的纸面上，只有正三角、正方、正六边形能无缝铺满。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hyperbolic-tiling",
      "section_id": "tiling",
      "line_id": "pq-3",
      "filename": "tiling-pq-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hyperbolic-tiling/tiling-pq-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.84,
      "size": 45504,
      "text": "而在双曲平面里，只要 p 减二乘以 q 减二大于四，就能镶嵌，方案有无穷多种。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hyperbolic-tiling",
      "section_id": "equal",
      "line_id": "eq-3",
      "filename": "equal-eq-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hyperbolic-tiling/equal-eq-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "缩小只是圆盘投影的错觉，相邻瓦片都由圆反演精确翻折而来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hyperbolic-tiling",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hyperbolic-tiling/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "庞加莱圆盘把无限的双曲平面，收进一个有限的圆里。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hyperbolic-tiling",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hyperbolic-tiling/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "有限中藏着无限，这正是双曲几何的浪漫，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
